{"tha-ap178:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap178:0.2":"Kumudavagga ","tha-ap178:0.3":"Maggadattikattheraapadana ","tha-ap178:1.1":"“Anomadassi bhagava, ","tha-ap178:1.2":"dvipadindo narasabho; ","tha-ap178:1.3":"Ditthadhammasukhatthaya, ","tha-ap178:1.4":"abbhokasamhi cankami. ","tha-ap178:2.1":"Uddhate pade pupphani, ","tha-ap178:2.2":"sobham muddhani titthare; ","tha-ap178:2.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap178:2.4":"vanditva pupphamokirim. ","tha-ap178:3.1":"Visakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap178:3.2":"ito panca jana ahum; ","tha-ap178:3.3":"Pupphacchadaniya nama, ","tha-ap178:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap178:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap178:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap178:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap178:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma maggadattiko thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap178:6.1":"Maggadattikattherassapadanam chattham. "}